`ft.Text`コントロールの`value`に格納","children":[]},{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81a9-9aff-c4ceac8bb332","type":"numbered_list_item","parent":"4. `ft.Text`コントロールを`update`する","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-810d-b7c0-dd531e7b9858","parent":"※ファイルは「flet-prac3.py」として保存","children":[]},{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8123-9c59-c3c31e4a10c9","type":"heading_1","parent":"# 進捗アンケート","children":[]},{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81aa-aec8-dafb6a31221e","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81a6-83e4-f87d39d43b71","parent":"この問題が終了した人は、以下のGoogleフォームに回答してください。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8110-b2d6-f9f4ce7c5ad9","parent":"回答後、練習問題の回答例のURLをメールでお送りします。","children":[]},{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8163-a603-fbef7ad47608","type":"quote","parent":"> ","children":[{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81e1-8616-f079aa45f2cf","type":"bookmark","parent":"[bookmark](https://forms.gle/FFBeAXNS5VA5AJV29)","children":[]},{"blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81b9-a4c8-c72951bd4602","type":"paragraph","parent":"c","children":[]}]}],"pageNavs":[{"title":"Home","id":"/posts"},{"title":"基礎班カリキュラム","id":"/posts/course/basic"},{"title":"前期","id":"/posts/course/前期"},{"title":"Flet","id":"/posts/post/flet-1"},{"title":"Fletの練習問題3","id":"/posts/post/flet-117d2297f-7a72-80f3-b72b-d2e514002c10"}],"parentTitle":"Flet","childNavs":[{"title":"2. カウンターを作ってみよう","id":"17d2297f-7a72-803c-829b-ea2844416a5c","child":true},{"title":"3. ページの生成","id":"17d2297f-7a72-80e6-8335-c5d7dabb7f09","child":true},{"title":"Fletの練習問題1","id":"17d2297f-7a72-80be-a21a-ef14a273a257","child":true},{"title":"5. コントロールのレイアウト","id":"17d2297f-7a72-80b3-8ec3-dee35809a987","child":true},{"title":"Fletの練習問題2","id":"17d2297f-7a72-8047-916c-c6e61be1cf17","child":true},{"title":"6. イベントハンドラと更新","id":"17d2297f-7a72-8059-844e-c8c6f6121e66","child":true},{"title":"Fletの練習問題3","id":"17d2297f-7a72-80f3-b72b-d2e514002c10","child":true},{"title":"電卓について","id":"1a02297f-7a72-808b